OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfsted: MPs call for an end
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto single-word grades      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, MPs have called for an end to          
OL,6, single-word Ofsted judgments after     
OL,7, school inspections.                    
OL,9,FThe cross-party education select       
OL,10,Fcommittee's report also said schools   
OL,11,Fshould not be automatically graded     
OL,12,F"inadequate" for minor safeguarding    
OL,13,Fconcerns.                              
OL,15,FBut it said most in the sector still   
OL,16,Fwanted "strong accountability" in      
OL,17,Fschools.                               
OL,19,FOfsted welcomed the report and said it 
OL,20,Fwould respond to its recommendations.  
